<p>
<lb n="1"/>śālivāhana śakaśaradaṁbulunu vēyeṇnūṭa tridaśakaṁbelama
<lb n="2"/>reṁḍu varapramōdūta saṁhṛtsara vaiśākhamāsa śu
<lb n="3" break="no"/>klatadiya mariyu bhānuvāramu mṛgaśira
<lb n="4" break="no"/><unclear>va</unclear>nara nakṣatraṁbu rāśi mēṣaṁbuna raṁmyamu
<lb n="5"/>ganu śrīkūrmanayakaśrīpādasa<unclear>nni</unclear>dhi danara cāma
<lb n="6" break="no"/>¨rtisītayaku vēdya suṁdarāpuravṛ¨rtti muṁdugā dha
<lb n="7" break="no"/>naṁbu kōri tā Icni dhīruḍavani mātṛgōtrōdbava maṁ
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ḍḍala taṁmmanna Arayaṁga nitya paṁcāmṛtaṁbu śu
<lb n="9" break="no"/>bhaguḍai migula bhūsurava<supplied reason="omitted">ru</supplied>l bogaḍaṁga nabhiṣēka mo
<lb n="10" break="no"/>niriṁce bhaktitōḍi Araya sahasranāma¨rcana cāma
<lb n="11" break="no"/>raṁbunu paṁkaṇamunu mari ghanasuraṁṭhiyu <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> <unclear>bho</unclear>gaśēvala
<lb n="12"/>ṣōḍaśōpacārasamētamaina pūjalu salpe mānyuḍagu
<lb n="13"/>cu Ācaṁdratārā¨rkamavaniyeṁduna putra pau
<lb n="14" break="no"/>trābhivṛ¨rdhiyai prajaliyuḍu yenucu vijñāna
<lb n="15" break="no"/>śāstraṁbu nelami cadivina bhūsurēṁdṛlu Ī rīti saṁ
<lb n="16" break="no"/>stutiṁppa vini kṛtā¨rthuḍanaiti nanvēḍu kalarā<supplied reason="omitted">ra</supplied> dharma
<lb n="17" break="no"/>midiyeni vinutiṁce dhāta divini <g type="danda">.</g> svadatādvi
<lb n="18" break="no"/>guṇaṁ puṇyaṁ paradattānupālanaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied><note n="443-1">The second half of this well known verse is omitted.</note>
